SAVING_THROWS: Display your saving throw bonuses

Syntax: saving_throws

DESCRIPTION:
  Displays your current bonuses to all Palladium saving throws:
    - vs. Magic (PE-based)
    - vs. Poison/Toxin
    - vs. Psionics (ME-based)
    - vs. Insanity
    - vs. Coma/Death (PE-based)
    - Horror Factor
    - vs. Possession/Transformation

  Bonuses increase with relevant attributes and OCC.

SEE ALSO: score, combat, stats
